trans-unit.source: Provides the arguments for the <see cref="M:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.OnEventCommand(System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventCommandEventArgs)" /> callback.
trans-unit.target: Fornece os argumentos para o retorno de chamada <see cref="M:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.OnEventCommand(System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventCommandEventArgs)" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the array of arguments for the callback.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a matriz de argumentos para o retorno de chamada.
Uma matriz de argumentos de retorno de chamada.

trans-unit.source: Gets the command for the callback.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o comando para o retorno de chamada.
O comando de retorno de chamada.

trans-unit.source: The identifier of the event to disable.
trans-unit.target: O identificador do evento a ser desabilitado.

trans-unit.source: Disables the event that have the specified identifier.
trans-unit.target: Desabilita o evento que tem o identificador especificado.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <paramref name="eventId" /> is in range; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se <paramref name="eventId" /> estiver no intervalo; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: You can turn off all events in an event listener by calling <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventCommandEventArgs.DisableEvent%2A> starting with `eventID` = 1 and continuing until <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventCommandEventArgs.DisableEvent%2A> returns `false`.
trans-unit.target: Você pode desativar todos os eventos em um ouvinte de evento chamando <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventCommandEventArgs.DisableEvent%2A> começando com `eventID` = 1 e continuando até <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventCommandEventArgs.DisableEvent%2A> retorna `false`.

trans-unit.source: The identifier of the event to enable.
trans-unit.target: O identificador do evento a ser habilitado.

trans-unit.source: Enables the event that has the specified identifier.
trans-unit.target: Habilita o evento que tem o identificador especificado.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <paramref name="eventId" /> is in range; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se <paramref name="eventId" /> estiver no intervalo; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: You can turn on all events in an event listener by calling <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventCommandEventArgs.EnableEvent%2A> starting with `eventID` = 1 and continuing until <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventCommandEventArgs.EnableEvent%2A> returns `false`.
trans-unit.target: Você pode ativar todos os eventos em um ouvinte de evento chamando <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventCommandEventArgs.EnableEvent%2A> começando com `eventID` = 1 e continuando até <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventCommandEventArgs.EnableEvent%2A> retorna `false`.
